'''2015年澳大利亞大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2015 Australian Grand Prix}}），官方名稱為'''2015年一級方程式賽車勞力士澳大利亞大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2015 Formula 1 Rolex Australian Grand Prix}}）<ref>{{cite web|title=2015 Formula 1 Rolex Australian Grand Prix|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/races/2015/Australia.html|work=formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|accessdate=2015-03-15|archive-date=2015-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601025512/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/races/2015/Australia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是2015年3月15日舉辦於[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]的一場[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]賽事。比賽在[[墨爾本大獎賽賽道|墨爾本大獎賽賽道]]進行，總計58圈。這是[[2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]的首場分站賽事，<ref name="15 calendar">{{cite news | title = World Motor Sport Council 2014 – Beijing | work = FIA.com | publisher = [[Fédération_Internationale_de_l'Automobile|Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile]] | url = http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2014-beijing | date = 2014-09-12 | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archive-date = 2015-08-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150807133814/http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-2014-beijing | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="15 calendar 2">{{cite news |title=World Motor Sport Council 2014 – Doha |work=FIA.com |publisher=[[Fédération_Internationale_de_l'Automobile|Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile]] |url=http://www.fia.com/node/9172 |date=2014-12-03 |accessdate=2015-03-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319200239/http://www.fia.com/node/9172 |archivedate=2015-03-19 }}</ref>同時也是自併入世界錦標賽後的第79屆[[澳大利亞大獎賽|澳大利亞大獎賽]]（追溯至1928年的{{le|1928年澳大利亞大獎賽|1928 Australian Grand Prix|100英里路賽事}}），以及該賽事第20次舉辦於墨爾本大獎賽賽道。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://en.espnf1.com/f1/motorsport/page/2597.html|title=A history of the Australian Grand Prix|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2015-03-20|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403131307/http://en.espn.co.uk/f1/motorsport/page/2597.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[梅賽德斯車隊|梅賽德斯]]車手[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]為這場比賽的衛冕冠軍。<ref>{{cite news |title=2014 Formula 1 Rolex Australian Grand Prix — Results |url=http://forix.autosport.com/gp.php?l=0&r=20140001&c=2 |work=FORIX |publisher=Autosport |date=2014-03-16 |accessdate=2015-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414005638/http://forix.autosport.com/login.php?l=0&p=gp.php%3Fl%3D0%7Cr%3D20140001%7Cc%3D2 |archive-date=2014-04-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>他的隊友[[路易斯·漢米爾頓|路易斯·漢米爾頓]]第四度於這條賽道奪得桿位。<ref name="AUS quali"/>漢米爾頓與羅斯堡最終分別以一、二名完賽，而首次為[[法拉利車隊|法拉利車隊]]出賽的[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]則取得第三名。<ref name="Barretto">{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/118069|title=Lewis Hamilton beats Nico Rosberg to win|first=Lawrence|last=Barretto|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2015-03-15|accessdate=2015-03-15|archive-date=2015-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316231343/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/118069|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2015/mar/15/australian-gp-f1-2015-live|title=Australian GP: F1 2015 – as it happened|date=2015-03-15|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=Guardian Media Group|first=Adam|last=Woolcock|accessdate=2015-03-16|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315182736/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2015/mar/15/australian-gp-f1-2015-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==賽事簡報==
===背景===
====車手變更====
[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫車隊]]在比賽兩周前宣布，該隊車手[[費爾南多·阿隆索|費爾南多·阿隆索]]因在[[加泰隆尼亞賽道|加泰隆尼亞賽道]]的第二次季前測試遭受腦震盪傷勢，將缺席這場大獎賽。醫師建議阿隆索先不要參加比賽，因為可能會造成更進一步的傷害。因而，他將由曾在[[2014年澳大利亞大獎賽|2014年澳大利亞大獎賽]]拿下第二名的儲備車手[[凱文·馬格努森|凱文·馬格努森]]頂替出賽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2015/3/16854.html|title=Alonso to miss Australian race on medical advice|work=Formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|date=2015-03-03|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-date=2015-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311211803/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2015/3/16854.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====馬諾瑪魯西亞車隊====
[[馬諾車隊|馬諾瑪魯西亞車隊]]在經過季前一段時間的破產管理，並靠著近期的一筆投資存活下來後，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/31127165|title=Marussia team could make Formula 1 return this season|first=Andrew|last=Benson|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2015-02-04|accessdate=2015-02-04|archive-date=2015-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311021201/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/31127165|dead-url=no}}</ref>帶著通過強制性碰撞測試，但未出席任何一場季前測試的賽車來到的墨爾本。瑪魯西亞也宣布了他們的車手為[[雷諾方程式3.5升系列賽|雷諾方程式3.5升系列賽]]車手[[威爾·史蒂文斯|威爾·史蒂文斯]]與[[羅伯托·梅里|羅伯托·梅里]]，而梅里則僅簽了一份單場賽事的合約。<ref name="Merhi">{{cite web|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/117975|title=Roberto Merhi to race for Manor F1 team in Australian Grand Prix|date=2015-03-09|accessdate=2015-03-09|work=Autosport.com|first=Glenn|last=Freeman|publisher=Haymarket Media Group|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314041621/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/117975|dead-url=yes}}</ref>然而，該隊並未參與任何一階段的練習賽，其後也未做出排位時間，使得賽場上剩下18輛車。

====薩伯車隊受到法律挑戰====
荷蘭車手[[吉多·范德加德|吉多·范德加德]]在比賽一周前，向{{le|維多利亞省高等法院|Supreme Court of Victoria}}提出對[[薩伯車隊|薩伯車隊]]的法律行動，以強制執行他與車隊在2014年6月達成給予他2015年賽季正賽車手席位的協議。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/31752616|title=Giedo van der Garde: Ex-Sauber test driver takes legal action|work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2015-03-05|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150307163503/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/31752616|dead-url=no}}</ref>這項法律行動是基於范德加德透過瑞士的{{le|國際仲裁|International arbitration}}在2015年3月2日所獲得的一份判決，也是他在車隊於2014年11月宣布正賽車手為[[马库斯·埃里克松_(赛车运动员)|马库斯·埃里克松]]與[[費利佩·納斯爾|費利佩·納斯爾]]後初步行動。<ref name="Allens">{{cite web|title=Client Update: The driver, the racing team, the Grand Prix and the court – high-speed arbitration enforcement in the Victorian Supreme Court|url=http://www.allens.com.au/pubs/arb/cuarb16mar15.htm|accessdate=2015-03-20|publisher=Allens|date=2015-03-16|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402104723/http://www.allens.com.au/pubs/arb/cuarb16mar15.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年3月11日，范德加德在獲得強制薩伯讓他在墨爾本上場的法院命令後勝訴。同日，薩伯公開聲明表示，他們不會讓范德加德駕駛賽車來危及車隊或是其他車手的安全，並指出在代表埃里克森與納斯爾的律師對判決提出上訴前，{{le|薩伯C34|Sauber C34|C34底盤}}已經是專為兩位車手量身訂做。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/03/11/sauber-will-not-risk-safety-after-van-der-garde-ruling/|title=Sauber will not risk safety after van der Garde ruling|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2015-03-10|accessdate=2015-03-10|archive-date=2015-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311230702/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/03/11/sauber-will-not-risk-safety-after-van-der-garde-ruling/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://adamcooperf1.com/2015/03/11/van-der-garde-case-drags-into-thursday-as-sauber-appeal-continues/|title=Van der Garde case drags into Thursday as Sauber appeal continues|first=Adam|last=Cooper|work=Adam Cooper's F1 Blog|publisher=[[WordPress|WordPress]]|date=2015-03-11|accessdate=2015-03-11|archive-date=2015-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311230226/http://adamcooperf1.com/2015/03/11/van-der-garde-case-drags-into-thursday-as-sauber-appeal-continues/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

上訴在隔日聆訊並遭到駁回。作為其論證的一點，薩伯認為范德加德的合約在國際汽聯合約認證委員會的同意下，已經於今年二月由該隊終止，且范德加德因與媒體討論相關事宜，已經違反了合約中的保密條款。<ref name="appeal specifics">{{cite news|url=http://www.speedcafe.com/2015/03/12/court-to-decide-van-der-garde-fate-this-afternoon/|title=Court to decide van der Garde fate this afternoon|work=Speedcafe.com|last=Howard|first=Tom|date=2015-03-12|accessdate=2015-03-12|archive-date=2015-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150313103441/http://www.speedcafe.com/2015/03/12/court-to-decide-van-der-garde-fate-this-afternoon/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>埃里克森與納斯爾的委任律師更進一步指出范德加德沒有經過正當的法律途徑，因為他們的客戶直到范德加德向法院提出申請才被告知預期的法律行動。<ref name="appeal specifics"/>然而，法院維持原判，允許范德加德參與這場比賽，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/03/12/sauber-loses-appeal-against-van-der-garde-judgement/|title=Sauber loses appeal against van der Garde judgement|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2015-03-12|accessdate=2015-03-12|archive-date=2015-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150313093916/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/03/12/sauber-loses-appeal-against-van-der-garde-judgement/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>而審訊則被延後至隔日，以審理范德加德的法律團隊對薩伯車隊主席{{le|摩妮莎·卡爾藤伯恩|Monisha Kaltenborn}}提出之蔑視法庭訴訟一案。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://adamcooperf1.com/2015/03/13/sauber-case-continues-but-agreement-could-be-close/|title=Sauber case continues but agreement could be close|first=Adam|last=Cooper|work=Adam Cooper's F1 Blog|publisher=[[WordPress|WordPress]]|date=2015-03-13|accessdate=2015-03-13|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315000523/http://adamcooperf1.com/2015/03/13/sauber-case-continues-but-agreement-could-be-close/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在法院宣布判決後的兩個小時，國際汽聯發布了一份出賽名單，列名埃里克森與納斯爾為薩伯的車手。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fia.com/sites/default/files/championship/documents/20150312/Formula%20One%20Australian%20Grand%20Prix%202015%20Document%20-%205_0.pdf|title=2015 Australian Grand Prix - Entry List|date=2015-03-12|publisher=[[Fédération_Internationale_de_l'Automobile|Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile]]|work=FIA.com|accessdate=2015-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150312173340/http://www.fia.com/sites/default/files/championship/documents/20150312/Formula%20One%20Australian%20Grand%20Prix%202015%20Document%20-%205_0.pdf|archive-date=2015-03-12|dead-url=no|format=PDF}}</ref>由於薩伯未服從法院判決，使其車隊資產存在著被查封的風險，<ref name="Allens"/>因而車隊的兩位車手在第一階段練習賽皆沒有上場。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/formula1/31748403|title = Australian Grand Prix first practice|date = 2015-03-13|accessdate = 2015-03-13|website = BBC Sport|publisher = [[British_Broadcasting_Corporation|British Broadcasting Corporation]]|last = Rose|first = Gary|archive-date = 2015-03-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150313232429/http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/formula1/31748403|dead-url = no}}</ref>不過，媒體猜測[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]為了避免對這項運動有更進一步的負面宣傳做出干預，<ref>{{cite news|title=Sauber Formula One team settles with van der Garde for $16 million|url=http://autoweek.com/article/formula-one/sauber-f1-teams-settles-van-der-garde-16-million|accessdate=2015-03-21|publisher=AUTOWEEK|date=2015-03-17|archive-date=2015-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320222410/http://autoweek.com/article/formula-one/sauber-f1-teams-settles-van-der-garde-16-million|dead-url=no}}</ref>讓埃里克森與納斯爾參加週五下午的第二階段練習賽。<ref name="FP2">{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/03/13/mercedes-leads-ferrari-in-second-practice/|title=Mercedes leads Ferrari in second practice|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2015-03-13|accessdate=2015-03-13|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315170223/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/03/13/mercedes-leads-ferrari-in-second-practice/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年3月14日，范德加德期望在未來能找到更長久的解決方案，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://adamcooperf1.com/2015/03/13/van-der-garde-and-sauber-reach-agreement-but-story-inot-over-yet/|title=Van der Garde and Sauber reach agreement but story not over yet|first=Adam|last=Cooper|work=Adam Cooper's F1 Blog|publisher=[[WordPress|WordPress]]|date=2015-03-14|accessdate=2015-03-14|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315012329/http://adamcooperf1.com/2015/03/13/van-der-garde-and-sauber-reach-agreement-but-story-inot-over-yet/|dead-url=no}}</ref>宣布他將放棄在墨爾本出賽，糾紛因而在週六暫時解決，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/van-der-garde-drops-legal-action--won-t-race-for-sauber-in-austr.html|title=Van der Garde won't race for Sauber in Australia|work=F1.com|date=2015-03-14|accessdate=2015-03-14|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315093222/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/van-der-garde-drops-legal-action--won-t-race-for-sauber-in-austr.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>薩伯車隊與其2015年新車手從而能夠完成週六的排位賽，並在週日正賽中在積分圈內完賽。

